            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "No, not for new units. Section 10AA required manufacture or provision of services to begin by 31 March 2021, so units starting after that date get no deduction. Units that commenced earlier continue the fifteen year phased benefit of 100%, then 50%, then 50% linked to a reinvestment reserve. GST zero rating and customs benefits are unaffected."
          }
